commit.message:
re PR bootstrap/69885 (ICE in maybe_legitimize_operand, at optabs.c:6903 on m68k-linux-gnu)

	PR target/69885
	* config/m68k/m68k.md (ashldi3, ashrdi3, lshrdi3): Use
	SImode for last match_operand.

	* gcc.dg/pr69885.c: New test.

From-SVN: r233603
